咁<br />\n用配樂夾硬托起套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好老實講, 好多位如果唔係配樂出色, 根本係悶場一個, 套戲係配樂救左佢啦"},{"pid":"237844127529ed733e02cbeb608592a8c5a0cdd5","tid":329310,"uid":29027,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T01:54:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>配樂如果有時停一停會好d</blockquote><br />\n走火入魔左<br />\n上一套已經係咁<br />\n用配樂夾硬托起套戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都覺得今次配樂過左火，好高頻 有d位甚至好刺耳<br />\n上次套intersteller都有類似既情況<br />\n<br />\n戴返個頭盔：唔覺得Dunkirk悶</blockquote><br />\n個啲ju87戰機嘅聲黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係現實中佢都係咁嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔了解歷史我唔怪你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f3731a7325a798df1e094a33c2f0ac08a2eafd4","tid":329310,"uid":29027,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T01:57:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>三條時間線係幾特別<br />\n但係對本身套戲既劇情同氣氛無咩幫助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果佢用線性敘述你又會話結局咁易估<br />\n冇深度 跟本上佢嘅剪接係想表達戰爭唔係一個人嘅事<br />\n戰爭從來都冇主角 失敗嘅比人當英雄<br />\n而真英雄就被俘虜永遠冇人知"},{"pid":"2860b5f12f7ef8a7ad5ed8300252d8628f071e7a","tid":329310,"uid":29027,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T01:58:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>走老就走老啦，大乜撚野行乜撚野動啫，岸鳩鳩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇睇下覺得幾搞笑<br />\n比人包圍 空中無乜支援<br />\n成班人上船比人炸完 又棄船 之後上第二架 關埋落艙入面等比魚雷炸 之後又棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢講到明係要還原歷史<br />\n你自己冇去了解歷史就胡亂批評<br />\n咁樣真係一個睇電影嘅人咩？"},{"pid":"31592a5560a84c5c81cd964525b9d1beed9b568a","tid":329310,"uid":109574,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T02:07:40.000Z","msg":